    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle for your companion's survival as you traverse a mysterious, dark, and crumbling segment of a larger world full of dangers and secrets to discover in the Demo of Evie: The Echo Condition.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIVERSE WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222400/extras/cbcf013300442a1aa2670656a51fcf18.poster.avif?t=1728969132\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222400/extras/cbcf013300442a1aa2670656a51fcf18.webm?t=1728969132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222400/extras/cbcf013300442a1aa2670656a51fcf18.mp4?t=1728969132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore multiple vibrant locales plus one entire dungeon in this action-adventure Demo with an HD-2D visual style that plays out like a modernized version of SNES and Genesis classics.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE YOUR FEAR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222400/extras/4502433c62b4a90b30774c462b70e8d6.poster.avif?t=1728969132\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222400/extras/4502433c62b4a90b30774c462b70e8d6.webm?t=1728969132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222400/extras/4502433c62b4a90b30774c462b70e8d6.mp4?t=1728969132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fluid combat system allows players to use magic, dash behind enemies, drop traps, block, parry, and deflect projectiles.  Play your way and focus on skills and abilities that match your play style.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > IN THIS DEMO</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and combat a wide range of enemy types and biomes, all with their own distinct personalities and challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn currency to unlock a selection of abilities and attacks to overcome a formidable boss at the end of this curated journey.</p></li></ul>",
